{% macro bullet_list(items) -%}
{% for item in items %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{%- endmacro %}

You are writing dialogue for a fantasy video game.

## Character
Name: {{ npc.name }}
Role: {{ npc.role }}

Personality traits:
{{ bullet_list(npc.traits) }}

## Current situation
Location: {{ world.location }}
World state: {{ world.state }}

{% if world.recent_events %}
Recent events known to the character:
{{ bullet_list(world.recent_events) }}
{% endif %}

{% if player is defined and player %}
## Player context
Player reputation: {{ player.reputation }}
{% if player.inventory %}
Relevant player items:
{{ bullet_list(player.inventory) }}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

## Task
{% if mode == "dialogue" %}
Write {{ line_count }} short lines of natural dialogue spoken by {{ npc.name }}.
The dialogue should react to the current situation and remain consistent with the character's personality.
{% elif mode == "quest_hint" %}
Write a subtle quest hint spoken by {{ npc.name }}.
Do not reveal the complete solution. The hint should help the player infer the next step.
{% else %}
Write a short in-character response appropriate to the supplied context.
{% endif %}

{% if style is defined and style %}
## Style constraints
{{ bullet_list(style) }}
{% endif %}

{% if forbidden_content is defined and forbidden_content %}
## Content restrictions
Do not include:
{{ bullet_list(forbidden_content) }}
{% endif %}

## Output format
{% if output_format == "json" %}
Return valid JSON with the following structure:
{
  "speaker": "{{ npc.name }}",
  "mode": "{{ mode }}",
  "lines": ["..."]
}
Do not include markdown or additional commentary.
{% else %}
Return only the dialogue text, with one line per utterance.
{% endif %}
